Module org.apache.jena.arq
Package org.apache.jena.riot.lang

Class TriX

java.lang.Object
org.apache.jena.riot.lang.TriX
public class TriX extends Object
TriX - see HPL-2004-56 Jeremy Carroll and Patrick Stickler. Supported:
  • Basic TriX as per the DTD in HPL-2004-56
  • Typed literal rdf:XMLLiteral with inline XML.
  • <qname> (on reading)
